With a self-adhering surface, the film is designed for easy installation and zero-to-minimal bubbles during application. A squeeze card is also included to remove the occasional bubble easily.Works with:Google Nexus 7 (2nd generation)(NOT compatible with the 1st Generation Nexus 7)Contains:2x Screen Protector , Micro-Fiber Cleaning Cloth, Squeeze cardColor:HD Clear (Invisible)Application:Each of the screen protectors contains 3 layers of PET film.
